<hymn_number>5247</hymn_number>
<title>lk ạlmjd llạ̉bd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- laka ạl̊maj̊du llạảbad̊
 yā yasūʿu rabãnā
 qad̊ ḥamal̊ta fī ạl̊jasad̊
 ại̹tẖ̊manā waḥuk̊manā

[V2]
 2- nub̊ta ʿanãạ yā ḥabīb̊
 ḥāmila ạl̊ḥuk̊mi ạlrãhīb̊
 dẖāka ḥuk̊munā waqad̊
 ạủk̊mila ʿalay̱ ạlṣãlīb̊

[V3]
 3- ḥubũka ạl̊ḥubũ ạl̊ʿajīb̊
 fāqa ại̹d̊rāka ạl̊ʿuqūl̊
 lam̊ yakun̊ haẘlu ạlṣãlīb̊
 dūna dẖā ạl̊ḥubĩ yaḥūl̊

[V4]
 4- fah̊wa kāl̊maẘti qawī̃
 nāruhu laẓay̱ ạlại̹lah̊
 lạa bisaẙliⁿ yan̊ṭafī
 ạảẘ bikatẖ̊raẗi ạl̊mīāh̊

[V5]
 5- laẙsa min̊ ḥadiⁿ̃ lahu
 ạảẘ qīāsiⁿ ạảẘ qarār̊
 kulũ fik̊riⁿ lil̊waray̱
 ʿin̊da dẖā ạl̊ḥubĩ yaḥār̊

[V6]
 6- falaka kulũ ạltẖãnā
 yā yasūʿu ạl̊muf̊tadī
 ại̹dẖ̊ manaḥ̊tanā ạlrãjā
 wāl̊kẖalạaṣa ạlạảbadī̃</lyrics>
</song>